ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, especially if this student is looking to finish both their prospectus and orals in the same year. This workshop keeps students working on thier prospectus while they read for orals. Having to submit bi-weekly asssignments ensures that I will not be working on my prospects at the end of my third year when my orals are complete. This would not be feasible since we have to circulate several drafts of our prospectus before we can schedule our colloquium.
An introduction to what the prospectus is, how to write it.
It's an easy way to get ahead on your dissertation thinking when you otherwise would not be giving yourself time to do so.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It has been central in developing my prospectus.
